                    <div class="container">
            <div class="text-wrapper">
              <div class="text">
                <div>
                  <h1>Create a Workspace</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="gold-border"></div>
                <div class="paragraph">
                  <p>
                    Potential customers often wonder how the solutions Packsize offers are going to impact their workspace and production line. We created a workspace editor tool inside their new sales app that enables them to build out a virtual workspace and visualize how their new packaging facility will look and function.                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="screenshot right">
